uest failed because it depended on another request and that request failed.","424_NAME":"FAILED_DEPENDENCY","425":"Too Early","425_CLASS":"4xx","425_MESSAGE":"The server is unwilling to risk processing a request that might be replayed.","425_NAME":"TOO_EARLY","426":"Upgrade Required","426_CLASS":"4xx","426_MESSAGE":"The client should switch to a different protocol such as TLS/1.0, given in the Upgrade header field.","426_NAME":"UPGRADE_REQUIRED","428":"Precondition Required","428_CLASS":"4xx","428_MESSAGE":"The origin server requires the request to be conditional.","428_NAME":"PRECONDITION_REQUIRED","429":"Too Many Requests","429_CLASS":"4xx","429_MESSAGE":"The user has sent too many requests in a given amount of time.","429_NAME":"TOO_MANY_REQUESTS","431":"Request Header Fields Too Large","431_CLASS":"4xx","431_MESSAGE":"The server is unwilling to process the request because either an individual header field, or all the header fields collectively, are too large.","431_NAME":"REQUEST_HEADER_FIELDS_TOO_LARGE","451":"Unavailable For Legal Reasons","451_CLASS":"4xx","451_MESSAGE":"A server operator has received a legal demand to deny access to a resource or to a set of resources that includes the requested resource.","451_NAME":"UNAVAILABLE_FOR_LEGAL_REASONS","500":"Internal Server Error","500_CLASS":"5xx","500_MESSAGE":"A generic error message, given when an unexpected condition was encountered and no more specific message is suitable.","500_NAME":"INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR","501":"Not Implemented","501_CLASS":"5xx","501_MESSAGE":"The server either does not recognize the request method, or it lacks the ability to fulfil the request. Usually this implies future availability.","501_NAME":"NOT_IMPLEMENTED","502":"Bad Gateway","502_CLASS":"5xx","502_MESSAGE":"The server was acting as a gateway or proxy and received an invalid response from the upstream server.","502_NAME":"BAD_GATEWAY","503":"Service Unavailable","503_CLASS":"5xx","503_MESSAGE":"The server is currently unavai